sentences.english: Ignoring those, the remaining central shape is nondescript.
sentences.chinese: 不顧這些，其餘的中央形狀是不倫不類。

sentences.english: In Chinese it also means “neither fish nor fowl”.
sentences.chinese: 在中文中，它還有“不倫不類”之意。

sentences.english: Setting ambitious plans without the ability to execute them will only result in performances that are unsatisfactory.
sentences.chinese: 眼高手低的結果，只能是不倫不類的演出。

sentences.english: The new garage made an awkward addition to the house.
sentences.chinese: 新建的汽車車庫與房子不相稱，有點不倫不類。
